Presenting gg_ducksoup.

Uses the typical style of mq textures,

This is an updated version of my very fist map. Includes destructible forts for both sides, underwater tunnels, sniper spots and baracades of all sorts to keep your team well guarded.

Perfect for short range weapons, long range weapons, knifing and hegrenades.

This map also has buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have this on any non-gungame server.

All textures created by myself.

Skybox texture credit goes to Karatek√§fer, thank you so much, your sky textures are priceless. They really add a lot to my maps.
